## Prerequisites

- .NET SDK {{targetFramework}} or higher

## Getting Started

### Restore dependencies
```bash
dotnet restore
```

### Run the service
```bash
dotnet run
```

### Build
```bash
dotnet build
```

### Test
```bash
dotnet test
```

## API Endpoints

- `GET /health` - Health check
- `GET /api/v1/hello` - Example endpoint
{{#if enableSwagger}}
- `GET /swagger` - Swagger UI
{{/if}}

## Configuration

Environment variables:
- `ASPNETCORE_ENVIRONMENT` - Environment (Development, Staging, Production)
- `ASPNETCORE_URLS` - Server URLs (default: http://localhost:5000)

## Docker

Build image:
```bash
docker build -t {{projectName}} .
```

Run container:
```bash
docker run -p 5000:5000 {{projectName}}
```

